<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <title>Offer accepted</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        .bg {background-color: #69a6c9;color: #000; padding: 15px}
        .text {background-color: #fff;color: #555555;}
        .container{padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;}
        .img{width: 100px;padding-top: 7px;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg"></div>
<div class="container text" style="text-align:center;">
    <i> Dear {{ first_name }},<br><br>

        Your Offer of {{ (offer/100)|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}{{currency_name}} has been accepted.
        Congratulations!<br>
        The product will be delivered to you by the postal service.
        Payment: Cash on delivery.<br>
        Thank you for your patience.<br>
        Bidding application </i><br><br>
</div>
<div class="bg"></div>
</body>
</html>